1
00:00:55,490 --> 00:00:56,590
Hello.

2
00:00:57,090 --> 00:00:59,890
Welcome to Bloody Game X.

3
00:01:00,560 --> 00:01:04,700
Bloody Game is
a very unfair and irrational game.

4
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:10,070
You may use lies, betrayals,
schemes, politics,

5
00:01:10,440 --> 00:01:12,710
or any other means to survive.

6
00:01:13,310 --> 00:01:15,280
As long as you don't break
Bloody Game's rules,

7
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:19,250
any action taken for survival
is justified.

8
00:01:34,060 --> 00:01:35,300
Darn it.

9
00:01:46,940 --> 00:01:47,980
What is this?

10
00:01:49,580 --> 00:01:50,780
What really surprised me...

11
00:01:51,450 --> 00:01:53,980
was that there were so many people.

12
00:01:54,520 --> 00:01:55,680
"Seong Beom is here?"

13
00:01:55,850 --> 00:01:57,890
"What? I see Xitsuh. I see Hye Seon."

14
00:01:58,090 --> 00:02:01,690
Then I began to notice the members
who were totally unexpected to be here.

15
00:02:02,060 --> 00:02:06,130
Kim Kyoung Hoon and Kim You Hyun
were sitting at the far end.

16
00:02:08,030 --> 00:02:10,300
What? Sang Min is here? Goodness.

17
00:02:11,530 --> 00:02:12,770
Sang Min...

18
00:02:12,870 --> 00:02:15,070
As for Sang Min, he and I...

19
00:02:15,070 --> 00:02:17,210
I think it's been around 12 or 15 years.

20
00:02:17,470 --> 00:02:20,480
We were on "The Genius" together
at the time.

21
00:02:20,480 --> 00:02:22,210
Ever since then,
he has never gone on a survival show.

22
00:02:22,210 --> 00:02:26,050
The guy I thought wouldn't be joining
was here,

23
00:02:26,050 --> 00:02:27,220
so I was really surprised.

24
00:02:27,450 --> 00:02:30,490
Overall, the members all seemed tough.

25
00:02:31,250 --> 00:02:32,650
I took a look at the guys,

26
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,890
and there was Kyoung Hoon
sitting next to me,

27
00:02:34,890 --> 00:02:36,620
and there were You Hyun and Jin Ho.

28
00:02:36,760 --> 00:02:38,660
"Gosh, with these members,"

29
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,430
"I could win."

30
00:02:40,660 --> 00:02:44,100
I thought, "I don't fall so far behind."

31
00:02:44,830 --> 00:02:46,370
I saw the people
sitting across from me first,

32
00:02:46,370 --> 00:02:48,140
and I saw the members
from the second season.

33
00:02:48,270 --> 00:02:51,140
I saw the second season members
like Seung Jin and YunB.

34
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:54,780
What was surprising was,
and excuse me for saying this,

35
00:02:54,780 --> 00:02:56,480
there were people
I saw for the first time...

36
00:02:56,480 --> 00:02:58,210
that I almost asked who they were.

37
00:02:58,310 --> 00:03:00,880
People whom I've never seen
on survival shows.

38
00:03:01,250 --> 00:03:03,550
I wondered how they ended up here.

39
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:11,230
The man sitting on my right
couldn't take his blindfold off,

40
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:12,830
so I helped him.

41
00:03:17,570 --> 00:03:18,630
What is this?

42
00:03:24,270 --> 00:03:27,140
Gwan Hee, the man with whom
I became the final couple...

43
00:03:27,140 --> 00:03:28,810
on "Single's Inferno," was here.

44
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:32,280
It never occurred to me that
I'd run into him at a place like this.

45
00:03:32,510 --> 00:03:33,780
So I was really flustered.

46
00:03:33,780 --> 00:03:36,620
I think that encounter had more impact...

47
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:39,350
than when I met her on "Single's Inferno."

48
00:03:43,420 --> 00:03:45,860
I will now tell you
the rules of Bloody Game X.

49
00:03:46,460 --> 00:03:47,900
Bloody Game X...

50
00:03:48,860 --> 00:03:50,730
is a team match.

51
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,400
A team match?

52
00:03:53,730 --> 00:03:58,270
Now, I'll introduce the five teams
participating in Bloody Game X.

53
00:03:58,770 --> 00:04:00,110
This is Team P1.

54
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:01,740
Park Ji Min.

55
00:04:01,740 --> 00:04:02,810
(Park Ji Min, anchor,
semi-final winner of Bloody Game 1)

56
00:04:02,940 --> 00:04:04,050
Lee Tae Gyun.

57
00:04:04,050 --> 00:04:05,510
(Lee Tae Gyun, police officer, lawyer,
final winner of Bloody Game 1)

58
00:04:05,710 --> 00:04:06,780
Jeong Keun Woo.

59
00:04:06,780 --> 00:04:08,320
(Jeong Keun Woo, former baseball player,
2008 Beijing Summer Games gold medal)

60
00:04:08,420 --> 00:04:10,020
And Lee Sang Min.

61
00:04:10,020 --> 00:04:11,650
(Lee Sang Min, TV personality,
"The Genius 2" winner)

62
00:04:11,820 --> 00:04:14,790
The players who left a great impression
on Bloody Game One...

63
00:04:15,020 --> 00:04:18,130
and a seasoned player
who sees through all the games...

64
00:04:18,430 --> 00:04:20,700
