65
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:22,730
This is Team P2.

66
00:04:23,530 --> 00:04:24,570
Ha Seung Jin.

67
00:04:24,570 --> 00:04:25,570
(Ha Seung Jin, former basketball player,
the first Korean to play in the NBA)

68
00:04:25,670 --> 00:04:26,670
Lee Jin Hyeong.

69
00:04:26,670 --> 00:04:27,900
(Lee Jin Hyeong, doctor,
the winner of Bloody Game 2)

70
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:29,040
Hyun Sung Joo.

71
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:30,100
(Hyun Sung Joo, pro poker player,
participated in WSOP 4 times)

72
00:04:30,340 --> 00:04:31,340
YunB.

73
00:04:31,340 --> 00:04:32,340
